Frequently Asked Questions
Are there really zero fees?
At Fastn, we believe businesses shouldn’t have to wait or pay to access money they’ve already earned. That’s why it doesn’t cost a penny to create an account and there are zero transaction fees when you use the Fastn platform to pay and get paid. If you decide to leverage some of our more premium payment features (like Fastn Flow, which lets you get paid before your client pays you) there may be a small service fee—
